<p>Ever wonder how Kerbals keep coming back? Forum user, esinohio spells it out in his rough cut of a Six Million Dollar Man parody. Jeb can be rebuilt. Better. Faster. Stronger…</p>

If one continues to replace the original biological parts with mechanical ones, eventually there will be very little, or no original parts left.

MechJeb
